suncertify.ui

Class Messages

  • java.lang.Object
    • suncertify.ui.Messages

  • public final class Messages
extends Object
    The class Messages defines all the titles, labels, tooltips, button texts, and any other messages displayed to the user through the GUI. This allows for common messages to displayed across multiple UI windows without duplicating strings by importing them statically where needed.
